docs {
  ## Update Vendor
  อัปเดตข้อมูลผู้ขายที่มีอยู่

  Updates an existing vendor/supplier record including addresses and contacts.

  ### Path Parameters
  | Name | Type | Description |
  |------|------|-------------|
  | `bu_code` | string | Business unit code |
  | `id` | string (UUID) | Vendor ID |

  ### Headers
  | Name | Required | Description |
  |------|----------|-------------|
  | `Authorization` | Yes | `Bearer {{access_token}}` |
  | `x-app-id` | Yes | `{{x_app_id}}` |

  ### Permissions
  - **Permission key**: `vendor_management.vendor:update`
  - **Roles**: Purchase

  ### Sample Body
  ```json
  {
    "code": "VND-2024-0001",
    "name": "Siam Fresh Co., Ltd.",
    "description": "Fresh produce and food ingredients supplier",
    "vendor_address": {
      "add": [],
      "update": [{ "id": "019638a6-...", "address_line1": "Updated address" }],
      "remove": []
    },
    "vendor_contact": {
      "add": [],
      "update": [{ "id": "019638a6-...", "phone": "0899999999" }],
      "remove": []
    }
  }
  ```

  ### Sample Response
  ```json
  {
    "data": {
      "id": "019638a6-2a00-7c4f-8e46-9b7a52c80c4d"
    },
    "paginate": null,
    "status": 200,
    "success": true,
    "message": "Success",
    "timestamp": "2026-04-29T08:30:00.000Z"
  }
  ```

  ### Error Responses
  | Status | When |
  |--------|------|
  | 401 | Missing or invalid bearer token |
  | 403 | User lacks `vendor_management.vendor:update` permission |
  | 404 | Vendor not found |
}

